title: HK airport on hunt for lost million
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › HK airport on hunt for lost million HK airport on hunt for lost million 13 hrs ago Read more: The New Zealand Herald 
On Friday, 13 bags containing $10 million were loaded on to flight CX198 in Auckland and transported to Hong Kong. Photo / Getty The hunt is on for $1 million after an botch-up during the unloading of 13 cash bags from a Cathay Pacific flight in Hong Kong.
